platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Learn secrets and historical facts about the world around you.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Whats that building? Which movie do I recognize this street from? Is there anything interesting to see around here? By pulling in relevant nearby information from Wikipedia, Inquire can answer all sorts of questions. Whether youre on vacation, have a spare half-hour while visiting an unfamiliar city, or just want to discover new things in your hometown, Inquire is the perfect pocket companion for curious minds.
